{"tid":539864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「讓我X給妳iPhone」　少女遭誘惑自拍裸照","createTime":"2018-01-25T02:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T08:59:00.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9a9c43032434d489161ad6b15f5298e219396e","tid":539864,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180125/640_e5f15c4638004ca16465a97eec409050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180125%2F640_e5f15c4638004ca16465a97eec409050.jpg&h=819912c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新北</span>市一名呂姓男子在網路搭訕未成年少女，以「iPhone加學費」為條件，拐騙少女自拍裸照傳給他。<br />\n <br />\n少女原本拒絕，卻禁不起對方再三誘惑，「都你啦，引出以前那個愛慕虛榮的我了」，配合脫衣拍照傳出。<br />\n <br />\n呂男食髓知味，進一步要求對方跟他發生性關係，少女拒絕後，擔心裸照外流，趕緊報警。<br />\n <br />\n由於雙方事後和解，新北地院依使未成年者性交易未遂罪，判呂6月徒刑，緩刑2年。（王嘉慶／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n今日新北連中2元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e743cf7e35ea6dd01d78eacd130c52ebea0c75de","tid":539864,"uid":137505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"所以話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32011a5ffd383724ce4b40a8363176aa1656599","tid":539864,"uid":738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"都你啦，引出以前那個愛慕虛榮的我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5996a0c38cbe7cc5680287ced79d1ccdafaeba27","tid":539864,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:56:43.000Z","msg":"新北+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm